      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK TOMMY (3) hit the ground running from out wide last start and crossed down to lead throughout (23.06) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 410m. Form reads well for this. PAW PALMER (6) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Hit the frame latest (25.53) when second at Warrnambool in a Grade 5 H. Looks well placed here and among the chances. PYRENEES ACE (5) could manage only third at this track last time but impressed when clocking a superb 23.12 over 410m at this track three starts ago. Has the ability and can find winning form again. PAW VORTEX (2) was below best last time at The Meadows (30.69) in a Special conditions race, finishing a 10 length seventh. Has already won three times from this draw.",
